# EvtGen user decay file.
#
# Forced signal decay:
#   Lambda_b0 -> Lambda0 gamma
# with Lambda0 forced to:
#   Lambda0 -> p+ pi-
#
# If you want to keep the physical Lambda0 branching ratios, remove the
# Lambda0 block and let it decay according to DECAY.DEC.

Decay Lambda_b0
  1.0 Lambda0 gamma PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-Lambda_b0

Decay Lambda0
  1.0 p+ pi- PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-Lambda0

End

